These are the below steps need to follow from the scratch

After creating the new server on ec2 instance or Aws Lightsail, you must update the system, this update will provide latest modifications on all the applications for your newly created instance.

######################################################################################################################################################################################################
# must use sudo infornt of your command to do this operation
sudo apt-get update 

# we are going to connect to MySQL database which is linked to your created instance and if you want to see the databases and tables inside the database server, install Sql-client from below command
sudo apt-get install mysql-client

# I worted code on python and related frameworks and dependencies need to be install to work the application properly.

sudo apt-get install python3
sudo apt-get install python3-flask
sudo apt-get install python3-pymysql
sudo apt-get install python3-boto3

# for running  python application, you must inside the folder which we have this Empapp.py file,
sudo python3 Empapp.py

All the best for your trials and keep me update the results :)

